<div style="font-size:40px; text-align:center; color:#383838;">Headquarters Hotel</div>
<br />
The headquarter hotel is the Hilton Garden Inn, 19677 East Jackson Drive, Independence, MO 64057 
1.800.445.8667, 816.350.3000, $95.00 per night, one king or two double beds. Call and mention 
Kansas City Classic Taekwondo for the room discount or go to <a href="http://www.hiltongardeninn.com">www.hiltongardeninn.com</a>, find the property by 
 the above hotel address, click Book a Room, enter the group code# KCC. The Hilton Garden Inn is located close to the Championship Venue and Gautreaux’s Martial Arts Center. It is a very nice hotel with several restaurants next door and a shopping mall a couple blocks away.
<br />
